Package: NFert
Title: N, P and K fertilization following Emilia-Romagna DPI 2026
Version: 0.14.0
URL: https://github.com/mcroci/NFert, https://mcroci.github.io/NFert/
BugReports: https://github.com/mcroci/NFert/issues
